//[Reference] 'Did you hear about that new console?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000100=新しいゲーム機の話を聞いたかい？
//[Reference] 'They say it only manages one teraflop...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000200=1テラフロップ性能しかないらしいけど…
//[Reference] 'Do you think it will be worth the investment?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000300=金を出す価値はあると思う？
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;Tomti^c:pop; is a skilled gamer.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000310=^c:1486b0;トムティ^c:pop;はスゴ腕のゲーマーなんだ。
//[Reference] 'We make a good team!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000320=僕たちはいいチームなのさ！
//[Reference] 'If only there was more time in a day.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000330=1日が24時間以上だったらいいのになぁ。
//[Reference] 'Or if only the nights were longer.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000340=それか、夜がもっと長かったらなぁ。
//[Reference] 'Have you seen any rare monsters around town?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000400=町の近くでレアモンスターを見かけなかった？
//[Reference] 'No, no, not real monsters... you know what, never mind.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000500=ああ、いや、本物のモンスターじゃなくてさ…なんでもないよ。
//[Reference] 'I'd love to go to one of those game conferences someday.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000600=いつか、ゲームの展示会やイベントに行きたいと思ってるんだ。
//[Reference] 'We're so far away from civilisation out here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000700=ここからじゃものすごく遠くてね…
//[Reference] 'No matter how many times I try, I can never get the characters I want...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000800=どれだけがんばっても、欲しいキャラが出てこないや…
//[Reference] 'I don't know why I keep playing these phone games.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10000900=どうしてこんなスマホゲーにはまっちゃったのかな。
//[Reference] 'Someday, I want to make my own game. I have the budget after all!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001000=いつか、自分でゲームを作りたいんだ。そのための金はあるよ！
//[Reference] 'I've been planning it for years now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001100=ゲームの構想は数年前から温めているんだ。
//[Reference] 'I have a six hundred page design document hidden away!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001200=秘蔵のデザインドキュメントは600ページもあるよ！
//[Reference] 'All I have to do now is learn how to program it...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001300=今の段階でやるべきことは、プログラミングを学ぶことだね…
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-s_name}^c:pop; can be pretty stubborn sometimes...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001400=^c:1486b0;{0-s_name}^c:pop;は時々頑固になっちゃうんだ…
//[Reference] 'All I want is to try out the time machine!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001500=どうしてもタイムマシンを試してみたいんだ！
//[Reference] 'I even offered to pay good money for the chance!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001600=そのためなら大金を出したってかまわない！
//[Reference] 'I refuse to believe it doesn't exist!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001700=タイムマシンが存在しないはずが無いからね！
//[Reference] 'Wouldn't it be cool if there was a scientist around here?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001800=近所に科学者がいたら、すごくクールだと思わない？
//[Reference] 'Some sort of professor with all kinds of wacky gadgets!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10001900=ヤバいガジェットばかり作ってるような天才系の人だよ！
//[Reference] 'Maybe they'd help me build my dream super robot!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002000=そういう人なら、夢に見たスーパーロボットを作る手助けもしてくれるかも！
//[Reference] 'The new expansion for my favourite MMO is launching soon!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002100=今はまってるMMOの最新拡張パックがもうすぐリリースだって！
//[Reference] 'I can't wait!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002200=待ちきれないよ！
//[Reference] 'I just hope they don't turn it into a gear treadmill again...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002300=でも、前みたいなアイテム収集ゲームじゃなければいいんだけど…
//[Reference] 'One of my online friends recommended a new book series to me.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002400=ネットの友達が新しい小説シリーズをおススメしてきたんだ。
//[Reference] 'I really can't remember what it was called though...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002500=でもその名前が思い出せなくて…
//[Reference] 'M-M- I think it started with M?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002600=たしかミ..何とかっていったかな。
//[Reference] 'Mist...something?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002700=ミスト…何とか、かな？
//[Reference] 'Why do I choose to play female characters in games?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002800=どうしてゲームで女キャラクターばかりやってるかって？
//[Reference] 'I get asked that a lot actually.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10002900=そのことをよく聞かれるんだ。
//[Reference] 'My answer is simple...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003000=その答えは単純さ…
//[Reference] 'Well, why not?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003100=そうしない理由はないからだよ。
//[Reference] 'Do you have a favourite boat?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003200=お気に入りの戦艦はある？
//[Reference] 'It's been a hot topic online for ages!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003300=長い間、ネットで話題になってるよ！
//[Reference] 'Mine's the Shimakaze by the way!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003400=ボクは「島風」がお気に入りだね！
//[Reference] 'The Amatsukaze is pretty cool too I suppose...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003500=でも「天津風」も悪くないかな…
//[Reference] ''Please look forward to it!''
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003600=「これからにご期待ください」
//[Reference] 'That's what he said...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003700=だってさ…
//[Reference] 'What a joke.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003800=何言ってんだか。
//[Reference] 'That was the worst reveal stream yet.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10003900=サイテーなおひろめ生放送だったよ。
//[Reference] 'People keep telling me the new Game of Seats book is coming soon.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004000=「ゲーム・オブ・シーツ」の新しい本が出るって言ってる人が多いんだけど…
//[Reference] 'That's the TV series!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004100=その名称はテレビドラマ版じゃないか！
//[Reference] 'Not the book!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004200=小説版じゃない！
//[Reference] 'The TV series! At least get them right!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004300=ドラマ版と小説版で違うんだよ！その辺わかってほしいんだ！
//[Reference] 'My favourite manga keeps going on hiatus.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004400=お気に入りのマンガが何度も休載するんだ。
//[Reference] 'It's been months now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004500=もう数ヶ月たったよ。
//[Reference] 'It comes off hiatus. Then goes back on hiatus a few days later.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004600=連載再開したと思ったら…ほんの数日でまた休載するって。
//[Reference] 'I don't even care any more. I just want it to end!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004700=ほんとにどうでもよくなってきたよ。ちゃんと最後まで連載してほしいよ！
//[Reference] 'Imagine being able to finish off monsters in one move!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004800=どんなモンスターもワンパンで倒せるようになれればなぁ！
//[Reference] 'That would be my dream super power!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10004900=自分が欲しい能力はそのパンチ力さ！
//[Reference] 'Now to just wait until I get pulled into another world!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005000=今すぐ異世界に飛ばされたりしないかな！
//[Reference] 'Just one more card!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005100=あと1枚！
//[Reference] 'I only need one more card to finish off my collection!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005200=それでやっとコレクションが完成するんだ！
//[Reference] 'The problem is it's a super rare promotional card...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005300=ただ、そのカードは激レアなプロモカードで…
//[Reference] 'No matter how much I'm willing to pay...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005400=いったいどれだけの金を出すことになるか…
//[Reference] 'I can't do much if no one is selling...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005500=出品すらされてないとどうにもならないし…
//[Reference] 'HB might be my favourite character of all time now...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005600=HBはボクの嫁、というか…
//[Reference] 'I played through the whole game in one sitting!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005700=ゲームを最初から最後まで一気にプレイしたくらいさ！
//[Reference] 'She's so perfect!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005800=ほんとサイコーだよ！
//[Reference] 'All the forums I frequent are flooded with fanart these days...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10005900=良く見るフォーラムはファンアートが投稿されてばかりで…
//[Reference] 'I just want to have good discussions and talk theories!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Nerd.line:10006000=ボクはファンアートよりも考察や話し合いをしたいんだよ！
